<p>
<seg id="1">Hurry up: Coach of Finnish World Championships athletes stuck in Helsinki</seg>
<seg id="2">Suren Ghazaryan, coach of long jumper Arttu Pajulahti and triple jumper Kristiina Mäkelä, is stuck in Helsinki, even though he should be coaching in the IAAF World Championships in Athletics in London.</seg>
<seg id="3">Kristiina Mäkelä may have to compete without hearing the advice of her coach.</seg>
