<seg id="3">Even a bucket can save the life of a drowning person.</seg>
<seg id="4">A drowning man was rescued in Tokoinranta, Helsinki, on Thursday.</seg>
<seg id="5">According to Ville Estlander, on-call fire and rescue officer from the Helsinki rescue department, the situation was quickly over.</seg>
