<seg id="3">Last year he was taken to the hospital for treatment to cuts on his wrists, which prison authorities said he sustained after falling in his cell.</seg>
<seg id="4">Pistorius was convicted of murder after an appeal by prosecutors against an initial manslaughter verdict.</seg>
<seg id="5">He killed Steenkamp in the early hours of Valentine's Day 2013 by shooting her multiple times through a toilet cubicle door at his Pretoria home.</seg>
