<seg id="1">Women's volleyball team on a par with Germany for two sets</seg>
<seg id="2">The Finland women's national volleyball team lost its fourth match in a World Championships qualifying tournament to Germany in straight sets 0–3 (23–25, 23–25, 14–25).</seg>
